## ‚ùå DON'T (Anti-patterns)

### Typography Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Random font sizes**: Don't use arbitrary sizes without scale
- ‚ùå **Too many sizes**: Don't use more than 7-8 sizes
- ‚ùå **Inconsistent weights**: Don't mix too many font weights
- ‚ùå **Poor readability**: Don't sacrifice readability for style

```css
/* ‚ùå Bad: Random sizes, no system */
h1 { font-size: 37px; }
h2 { font-size: 29px; }
h3 { font-size: 22px; }
p { font-size: 15px; }
small { font-size: 11px; }

/* ‚úÖ Good: Consistent scale (1.25 ratio) */
h1 { font-size: 3.052rem; }
h2 { font-size: 2.441rem; }
h3 { font-size: 1.953rem; }
p { font-size: 1rem; }
small { font-size: 0.8rem; }
```

### Spacing Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Random spacing**: Don't use arbitrary margin/padding values
- ‚ùå **Inconsistent spacing**: Don't mix spacing systems
- ‚ùå **No whitespace**: Don't pack elements too tightly
- ‚ùå **Too much spacing**: Don't separate related elements

```css
/* ‚ùå Bad: Random spacing values */
.card { padding: 17px; margin-bottom: 23px; }
.button { padding: 9px 21px; }
.section { margin-top: 47px; }

/* ‚úÖ Good: Consistent 4px-based system */
.card { padding: var(--spacing-4); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6); }
.button { padding: var(--spacing-2) var(--spacing-5); }
.section { margin-top: var(--spacing-12); }
```

### Color Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Too many colors**: Don't create rainbow interfaces
- ‚ùå **No hierarchy**: Don't use same color weight everywhere
- ‚ùå **Poor contrast**: Don't use similar shades for text and background
- ‚ùå **Color-only hierarchy**: Don't rely solely on color differences

```css
/* ‚ùå Bad: Everything equally prominent */
h1, h2, h3, p, small {
  color: #000000;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* ‚úÖ Good: Clear color hierarchy */
