```

### Layout Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Flat hierarchy**: Don't make everything same size/weight
- ‚ùå **Too many focal points**: Don't emphasize everything
- ‚ùå **Ignoring reading patterns**: Don't fight natural eye movement
- ‚ùå **No grouping**: Don't separate related elements

