- ‚ùå **Everything bold**: Don't bold everything important
- ‚ùå **All uppercase**: Don't overuse uppercase text
- ‚ùå **Too many highlights**: Don't highlight too many elements
- ‚ùå **Competing elements**: Don't create multiple primary CTAs

