Before launching, verify:
- [ ] Clear primary focal point on each page
- [ ] Consistent type scale across entire site
- [ ] Spacing follows consistent system (4px or 8px base)
- [ ] Color hierarchy: primary > secondary > tertiary
- [ ] Important actions visually prominent
- [ ] Related elements grouped together
- [ ] Adequate whitespace around key elements
- [ ] Headings form clear outline structure
- [ ] Text contrast meets WCAG standards (4.5:1 minimum)
- [ ] Visual weight matches content importance
- [ ] No competing elements for attention
- [ ] Natural reading flow (F or Z pattern)

